---
// About section component
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 px-4 md:px-8 lg:px-16">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <!-- About Image -->
      <div class="aspect-[4/5] bg-light-brown/10">
        <img
          src="/images/about/profile.jpg"
          alt="Grace King"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>

      <!-- About Content -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif mb-6">About Grace</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6 text-light text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            A life long admirer of creation + art. An eager student of all things beautiful and enriching. My own family is my greatest source of inspiration as it has helped me see the value of those relationships.
          </p>
          <p>
            This inspiration trickles into my sessions, as I see you first hand through the lens of my own motherhood. My sessions go beyond the typical smile and pose photoshoot. I see each as a blank canvas, ready to be made into something beautiful.
          </p>
          <p>
            They are a place of co-creation and collaboration between the two of us, as we artfully approach your session with intention. This honest and genuine approach curates a session of artful imagery that truly become an irreplaceable heirloom.
          </p>
        </div>
        <a
          href="#contact"
          class="inline-block mt-8 px-8 py-3 bg-light-brown text-white font-medium uppercase tracking-wider hover:bg-light-brown/90 transition-colors"
        >
          Work With Me
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
